700326f-a.title: Bronx: 211th Street - White Plains Road
700326f-a.text:
(1)
East 211th Street, east from but not including White Plains Road to and including Holland Ave., showing the 2-story house which stood at 727-729 East Gunhill Road, being moved from its original location.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, near Holland Ave., showing the method by which the house is being moved. The 4-story house prominently seen is No. 3514 Holland
Ave., at the S.E. corner of East 211th Street.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
700326f-a.folder: 211th Street & White Plains Road, Bronx, NY
